git clone <url> → Copy a remote repository to local
git status → Show current changes status
git add <file> → Add file(s) to staging area
git add . → Add all files to staging
git commit -m "msg" → Save changes with message
git log → Show commit history
git remote add origin <url> → Connect to GitHub repo
git push origin <branch> → Upload code to main
Git → Tracks code changes and helps manage versions locally.
